00:08:58.570 --> 00:09:02.240 align:middle line:10%
And I think life is just sort of
an ongoing process of reaching

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:04.310 align:middle line:10%
out into the darkness
when you really don't

00:09:04.310 --> 00:09:07.650 align:middle line:10%
