00:09:26.730 --> 00:09:28.890 align:middle line:90%
our higher potential.

00:09:28.890 --> 00:09:31.650 align:middle line:84%
This is truly what
humanity was built upon,

00:09:31.650 --> 00:09:34.200 align:middle line:84%
all those explorers
and mariners that

