We're not all going to face our
fears to the same magnitude.

00:09:51.680 --> 00:09:53.850 align:middle line:84%
But we are all given
the same hardware.

00:09:53.850 --> 00:09:56.120 align:middle line:84%
We are all set up
in the same way.

00:09:56.120 --> 00:09:58.990 align:middle line:84%
So it is possible for
every single one of us

00:09:58.990 --> 00:10:01.250 align:middle line:90%
