00:10:56.990 --> 00:10:58.070 align:middle line:90%
Very curious.

00:10:58.070 --> 00:11:02.330 align:middle line:84%
So is the shamanic state
and the psychedelic state

00:11:02.330 --> 00:11:08.340 align:middle line:84%
encrypted into our DNA, written
